title: Livin Fire - Under The Spell (EP 2013 oldschool hard rock heavy)
description:
Livin Fire is an igneous band from Cracow (Poland) playing the mix of hard rock and melodic heavy metal, inspired mostly by classics of the 80s. It shines out thanks to characteristic, strong female vocal and dynamic, full of energy solos being a real trade mark of the band. 
Under The Spell is the EP from 2013 that contains 6 new tracks by Livin Fire.
Check the band at facebook as well.
